{"tid":793400,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解仲會有人信鬼存在？（2）","createTime":"2018-08-25T11:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T05:28:17.000Z","uid":4450,"like":22,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fc06b087f4a0019f215932e8b92d388c91b29ad8","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:40:34.000Z","msg":"上一個post 超過9成人都係叫d唔信鬼既去玩咩 碟仙 去和合石 去唔知咩咩猛鬼既地方 <br />\n<br />\n之後有巴打試過玩碟仙冇見到鬼 隔離post有巴打去左好多佢地講既猛鬼地方又冇鬼<br />\n<br />\n仲有位信鬼既巴打話 和合石都冇鬼次次去都冇 仲話要去咩咩醫院先有<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">證明就算係見到鬼個班人其實都好矛盾 </span><br />\n想叫人去邊到做乜野for撞鬼既巴打可以省翻啖氣<br />\n<br />\n同埋鬼係唔被正式認同存在的 所以想話鬼存在既巴打應該拎證據出黎 而唔係叫唔相信鬼存在既人拎佢唔存在既證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aba479aba64ba13a601053fb06be2f12522fedb","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":11,"dislike":7,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:43:58.000Z","msg":"我就話 好多成日見鬼既人應該係有精神病<br />\n<br />\n而且香港有7份1人有精神病<br />\n<br />\n成日見鬼既巴打好快快睇醫生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e51c319c6a33dcebb09f7f2f8621efc04c20174","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:48:11.000Z","msg":"其實鬼 , 陽氣，陰氣，風水 係連埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw lm 等睇樓豬而一敵百"},{"pid":"d9680bd866164ceccb07593bfac4681a5832940d","tid":793400,"uid":120935,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T11:53:56.000Z","msg":"小心連登大法師皇天擊殺你"},{"pid":"7956f63daf3ff255605fd08b893eeb24405c8b7e","tid":793400,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:05:47.000Z","msg":"全部都係我創造岀黎"},{"pid":"9f8ece429e69d45ddc17ae05422b5313b30fcaff","tid":793400,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Bp5c3hBrZcM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBp5c3hBrZcM&d=epuV7h1PkwigIBzzVZ7YDEkviA