立場，例如你手拎住把有血刀，隔離有條屍，但客觀情況下，你未必係凶手，唔通我即刻話你係殺人犯？你暫時依然係良好市民，除非我有證據話你殺人，同理，係客觀情況下，冇任何證據說明有鬼，所以自然立場暫時歸係冇鬼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/spot/w600/201712/20180319133746_19_1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fspot%2Fw600%2F201712%2F20180319133746_19_1.JPG&h=427a7e76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d580f87e3b3c864653bac1da32809e912f9afdd7","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff96002a66dc99bb0ac2c37bf56a9c253460922","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79760a97a896ae45c1b9b804debad569a6aad821","tid":793400,"uid":127292,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8143362c39343487f1b23eef464dc3a3e3085324","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T19:35:06.000Z","msg":"點證明有？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T21:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"咁你證明到比卡超唔存在？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/spot/w600/201712/20180319133746_19_1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fspot%2Fw600%2F201712%2F20180319133746_19_1.JPG&h=427a7e76&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86d4f67ef6e8235373110b1ae32d1c162e0dd7b0","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c36f7c1812bd128d0238df5532b879b8a14b2b5e","tid":793400,"uid":48887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"信唔信應該係一個意願黎，無人逼到你信或者唔信<br />\n而證據係用黎證實樣野存唔存在，如果確實左係存在，就唔存在於信同唔信嘅概念而係有同無嘅概念。若人類已證明到100%有鬼，到時只係告知你一個事實，無存在信唔信嘅問題，無論你信唔信，果樣野都係存在。<br />\n<br />\n猶其呢一類未證明到係真定假，存唔存在嘅問題，就只能夠睇你個人個信念係點樣啦。<br />\n唔信者可以當佢故事咁睇，信者可以當係存在，注意返(當喳)未證實到架..你都唔可以逼到人地信你所講，除非你有證據100%證明，反之你又唔可以逼人地唔信，因為你又唔能夠100%證明佢唔存在..<br />\n<br />\n當然啦每樣野出現都有佢嘅原因，可能經過唔同嘅傳遞而令樣野/件事變質，到今時今日未必係100%準確，可能真確度只係得返1-2%.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"agree 樓主選擇性失明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cac48cbf917fc8cf5909ba77f5d8f7dac01d0246","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d580f87e3b3c864653bac1da32809e912f9afdd7","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff96002a66dc99bb0ac2c37bf56a9c253460922","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79760a97a896ae45c1b9b804debad569a6aad821","tid":793400,"uid":127292,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T21:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"咁你證明到比卡超唔存在？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.ulifestyle.com.hk/cms/images/spot/w600/201712/20180319133746_19_1.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fcms%2Fimages%2Fspot%2Fw600%2F201712%2F20180319133746_19_1.JPG&h=427a7e76&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:18:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"626b89bfe0121cd39056e54187aa65bd52206220","tid":793400,"uid":88840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d580f87e3b3c864653bac1da32809e912f9afdd7","tid":793400,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff96002a66dc99bb0ac2c37bf56a9c253460922","tid":793400,"uid":4450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79760a97a896ae45c1b9b804debad569a6aad821","tid":793400,"uid":127292,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T21:55:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:12:12.000Z","msg":"咁你證明到比卡超唔存在？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:09:53.000Z","m